## Title

Need a Personal or Company Website?  We're here to help. 

## Body

Freethining IT (on the web: freethinking.it) is a small, independent software consulting company started by two technology 
enthusiasts.  We believe that great customer relationships and a unified vision is key to overall product success. 

When working with new clients, no matter the size of the project, we'll work with you one-on-one to get to know your personal 
style and vision, and use those inputs to make the best possible product that works for YOU. 

We've worked with a number of clients ranging from high-profile/Forbes-Top-25 comapnies, to small start ups, to businesses
made up of one. 


